            "success": "The enemy is unaffected.",
            "failure": "For 1 minute, the wearer\u2019s allies within the glorious plate\u2019s 10-foot radius of light are \nconcealed\n to the enemy. Allies are concealed only while they remain within the light; if allies enter the light later, they are concealed as well.",
